                <pb facs="nei.j4c.39.1-5_0005b"/>
                
                <note type="authorial"><hi rend="underline">Later</hi>
                
                <p>I've taken the India matter up with the Washington office. The official here is very encouraging.</p>
                    
                Dr<hi rend="underline">s.</hi>N.</note>
                
